task.summary: Initial commit. Basic functionality for pre-processing emulated control data made available in this release.
Added basic logic for RNN using LSTM, more static emulated data for testing.
This closes #6, closes #9, and closes priscillaboyd/SPaT_Prediction#11
Added data processing for scikit-learn usage, implemented random forest ensemble, added module for initial data analysis/visualisation
Added ability to create sklearn dataset to DataPreProcessing, tidy up of CART (Decision Tree) algorithm implementation
Minor modifications to messages printed out to the user
